{"tid":1625543,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"arc呢間領養機構","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:11:00.000Z","uid":148574,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb9ce42b31341aea249a22a55dd176f384a8450","tid":1625543,"uid":148574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"領養機構竟然可以做到咁商業化👍🏻<br />\n<br />\n所謂嘅領養狗，自問屋企養咗兩次狗（上一隻狗係18歲自然老走），竟然同我講考試唔合格。而佢份考試其中一欄係要人捐錢=優先考慮申請，答覆係之前比嘅錢係「自願捐款」，就算唔批俾你養狗，亦都冇得退返。<br />\n<br />\n用一個考試唔合格嘅原因reject，就可以將隻狗keep返再嚟用另一個領養嘅人捐錢。 <br />\n<br />\n唔介意正正經經捐錢幫流浪狗，但前提你係真心幫到啲狗，同埋唔好攞嚟做「優先考慮申請」嘅頭號但背後想利用佢哋賺錢囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nh0pnVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNh0pnVk.png&h=5f1dc3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4SrBfm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4SrBfm.png&h=26d9f9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQuaitH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQuaitH.png&h=906e7667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOTa2Vq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOTa2Vq.png&h=d2a89fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV6748L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV6748L.png&h=18da2bd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fbe39470093a831465873986b61e5f6e4417b2","tid":1625543,"uid":148574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccb9ce42b31341aea249a22a55dd176f384a8450","tid":1625543,"uid":148574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:18:39.000Z","msg":"領養機構竟然可以做到咁商業化👍🏻<br />\n<br />\n所謂嘅領養狗，自問屋企養咗兩次狗（上一隻狗係18歲自然老走），竟然同我講考試唔合格。而佢份考試其中一欄係要人捐錢=優先考慮申請，答覆係之前比嘅錢係「自願捐款」，就算唔批俾你養狗，亦都冇得退返。<br />\n<br />\n用一個考試唔合格嘅原因reject，就可以將隻狗keep返再嚟用另一個領養嘅人捐錢。 <br />\n<br />\n唔介意正正經經捐錢幫流浪狗，但前提你係真心幫到啲狗，同埋唔好攞嚟做「優先考慮申請」嘅頭號但背後想利用佢哋賺錢囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nh0pnVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNh0pnVk.png&h=5f1dc3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4SrBfm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4SrBfm.png&h=26d9f9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQuaitH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQuaitH.png&h=906e7667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOTa2Vq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOTa2Vq.png&h=d2a89fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gV6748L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgV6748L.png&h=18da2bd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"有無人都試過中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbae87dbdd54e04eff9947ac26c446e86d794933","tid":1625543,"uid":245896,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"間野成日俾人話假領養真賣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fb一search有好多"},{"pid":"488b534b89910192a7336c2611944c349f9c41b4","tid":1625543,"uid":208663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"呃狗人"},{"pid":"baab14e7cd25b3a42624e50127de2b0efc6d4498","tid":1625543,"uid":148574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbae87dbdd54e04eff9947ac26c446e86d794933","tid":1625543,"uid":245896,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"間野成日俾人話假領養真賣狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fb一search有好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"早知一係search 一search先<img 